message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet the highest standards. This product comes with a unique set of features that promise to enhance your experience significantly. Considering its quality and the benefits it offers, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $18000. I believe this is a fair deal considering the value it brings. Please let me know if you have any questions or need more information about the product.
